---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | GOSQO" description="Privacy Policy for GOSQO AI Chat & Store Assistant.">
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="meta">Effective date: February 26, 2026</p>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>GOSQO AI Chat & Store Assistant is a Shopify application providing AI-powered chat, inbox, and content tools.</p>

    <h2>Information We Access</h2>
    <p>When installed, the app may access store information, products, orders, and customer communication data as needed.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Live chat and inbox functionality</li>
      <li>AI-assisted responses and content suggestions</li>
      <li>SEO audits and product content analysis</li>
      <li>Billing and subscription management</li>
      <li>Security and reliability</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>AI Processing</h2>
    <p>Some data may be processed by third-party AI providers to generate responses and content suggestions.</p>

    <h2>Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
    <p>Data is retained only as long as necessary. Upon uninstallation or verified request, associated data is deleted per Shopify requirements.</p>

    <h2>Security</h2>
    <p>We use reasonable measures including encryption in transit and access controls.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>privacy@gosqo.com</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>